<div class="quotetitle">Mills wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />Then, How can i use the consoleDrawText function from pvsneslib to write text in sprites?<br /></div><br />You can't.<br />You need to put your text into a table, according to the tiles of your text and then transfert it to VRAM after a vblank.<br />Just take a look in pvsneslib in vbl function, you will see how I send text to vram during a vblank (it is in console.c, in consoleVblank function).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5277">alekmaul</a> — Fri Jul 25, 2014 10:18 pm</p><hr />
